@node AESTH "Aesthir Glider"

@{b}Aesthir Glider@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = AI(C2)
Type    = Artifact Creature (2/1)
Cost    = 3
Artist  = Ruth Thompson / Ruth Thompson

@{b}NOTE@{ub}: There are TWO different artworks for this card.

Text(AI): Flying
          Cannot be assigned to block.

Flavor Text: @{i}"A fine example of the rewards of artifice: a thoroughly
              obedient steed with wings of Soldevi steel."
              ---Arcum Dagsson, Soldevi Machinist@{ui}

Flavor Text: @{i}"Sacrilege ! A noble ally in life, made nothing more
              than a glorified kite in death !"
              ---Arna Kennerud, Skycaptain@{ui}

