@node PHPOR "Phyrexian Portal"

@{b}Phyrexian Portal@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = AI(R2)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 3
Artist  = Pete Venters

Text(AI): <3>: Target opponent looks at the top ten cards of your
          library and separates them into two face-down piles.
          Choose one of those piles and remove it from the game.
          Search the remaining pile and put one of those cards
          into your hand. Shuffle the remaining cards into your
          library. Ignore this effect if you have fewer than
          ten cards in your library.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_P.guide/PHYPO}

@endnode
